headline.main: WINDSORS TO LEAVE FOR MIAMI TOMORROW; Starting Back to Nassau After a Two Weeks' Visit

lead_paragraph: The Duke and Duchess of Windsor will leave for Nassau via Miami at 10:30 tomorrow morning, it was announced yesterday, after what will have been a visit of exactly two weeks.
abstract: Duke of Windsor siens Victoria's Birthday Book to aid Bundles for Brit
